{"tid":1305871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"置頂！以傘為兵！全民武裝的時代到了！諸君聽我一言！","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T03:37:07.000Z","uid":4396,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"599e1615cc60e58273282120d9a6a9e66318e627","tid":1305871,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:21:00.000Z","msg":"有鑒於最近多名戰友比人無故襲擊，我認為有必要保護好自己！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我正式呼籲所有人由今日起出門帶一把遮！不論直遮或縮骨遮！<br />\n<br />\n遮：進可嚇退敵人，退可擋著一切攻擊！攜帶方便而不犯法！我認為這是最佳防身用具！<br />\n<br />\n勇武不代表破壞！而是勇於面對恐懼！你唔想反擊或傷害他人，你都要識點樣保護自己和戰友！你係可以擋住攻擊的！<br />\n<br />\n我希望今天起社會風氣要開始變，我地面對不作為的警察同咄咄逼人的藍屍，我地只能自己保護自己！<br />\n<br />\n最後！祝大家武運昌隆，忽忘五大訴求！忽忘烈士的寄望！<br />\n<br />\n你同意我建議就幫忙share出去！和理為盾，勇武為劍！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PfFo0fe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfFo0fe.png&h=62cdd6ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f4f47ee1f33320afa62c9689aa0a0648d08de4d","tid":1305871,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"642d15e797e6928416b7762cb992c4ca6a0607a7","tid":1305871,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:25:06.000Z","msg":"我認為我們一定要識點保護自己！"},{"pid":"92a3b0e8e9c0df81d0794d0129c546e95fee8722","tid":1305871,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:26:01.000Z","msg":"正正因為我地冇武器我地更需要替代品！"},{"pid":"bf69bc3f04cde2b0cb076f26a78360c0d2546d5e","tid":1305871,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"你可以唔攻擊人，但你一定要識保護自己和戰友！"},{"pid":"c6e03980fbacd1413ed45519dd7e67d6d37db6ce","tid":1305871,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"和理非和勇武一起面對！ 我地不分彼此！"},{"pid":"e05544c820537475cc02c72d2eac79c6835f9afd","tid":1305871,"uid":149361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:31:41.000Z","msg":"我覺得 有時比人打 反而對件事有好處"},{"pid":"49f7da88b4b28be58abfd6d67cc36a1632a75b88","tid":1305871,"uid":206268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:33:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ade1d80e00b95b0008a05a58d68038b81f1362f3","tid":1305871,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e05544c820537475cc02c72d2eac79c6835f9afd","tid":1305871,"uid":149361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:31:41.000Z","msg":"我覺得 有時比人打 反而對件事有好處"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:33:46.000Z","msg":"但你要識點減低傷害！唔係所有人都抗打！"},{"pid":"f252c00ae4d690fb8b572e3b8f699bd698a56688","tid":1305871,"uid":268855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da25c1418495edaf8f48e4a67bf2324d1b3bc661","tid":1305871,"uid":184195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"我兵你老母 帶傘純粹係為為左遮雨咋<br />\n香港天氣咁差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5e1bf30bbfb124a71707af2e497c75aea7de14","tid":1305871,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da25c1418495edaf8f48e4a67bf2324d1b3bc661","tid":1305871,"uid":184195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"我兵你老母 帶傘純粹係為為左遮雨咋<br />\n香港天氣咁差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"係呀！香港天氣咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />帶遮好合理"}]}